# Terraform working files and anything holding secrets or state — never commit.
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
terraform.tfvars
*.auto.tfvars
override.tf
override.tf.json
# Source bundle built by deploy.sh (git archive of the committed tree).
terraform/.build/
# The committed provider lock (.terraform.lock.hcl) is intentionally NOT ignored.
